content:
The impact of TTF on utilization is shown via a link between task-technology fit and beliefs about the consequences of using a system. This
is because TTF should be one important determinant of whether systems are believed to be more useful, more important, or give more relative advantage. All of these related constructs have been shown to predict utilization of systems (Davis, 1989; Hartwick and Barki, 1994;
Moore and Benbasat, 1992)
